{
  "stem": "10710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So I had already two-- two deadly sickness that I survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I was-- I was working in the Deutsche Emailwarenfabrik there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The camp was not as bad as any concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because we had better food to eat, and we were not afraid for the Germans-- for the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because even Goeth used to come, and Schindler was with him, he wouldn't touch anybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He had strict orders from Schindler not to touch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he said, out of the camp, you are the boss.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "In the camp, I am the boss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I remember one day I was going from-- from the barracks to the work, and here comes Schindler with Goeth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And it was-- the ground was very muddy, was raining.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "There was a lot of mud outside, and his boots were all dirty, Goeth's.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He saw me, he says, come here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Clean my boots.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So I had-- with my finger, I cleaned my-- and I was lucky that Schindler was there, because if Schindler wasn't there, I would be finished with him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Because he-- after whatever you do, he shot you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So Schindler says, lauf.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Run away already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "This was my encounter with Goeth for the first time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But you see, in Plaszow, in the Deutsche Emailwarenfabrik, Schindler was the boss.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So even the SS men who was watching us, they could not come to the camp to do anything bad to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So everybody was survived-- and everybody survived in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "There were families there are from Krakow-- father, husband and wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they had all easy work, because most of the people were from Krakow, so each-- everybody knew each other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "We were the newcomers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "We were from other towns, so we did all the heavy work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "They had the work in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
